'''Al Wifaq''' ({{lang-ar|'''الوفاق'''}}) was a [[Morocco|Moroccan]] [[Jew]]ish [[nationalist]] organization promoting coexistence between Jews and [[Muslim]] communities in [[Morocco]].

Al Wifaq was established in February 1956 and stopped its activities the same year following the removal of the Jewish minister of Telegraphs ([[Benzaquen|Dr. Benzaquen]]) and the sudden prohibition on [[Aliya|Jewish emigration]] to [[Israel]].

